↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiyHapN","text_ar":"صَبِيحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, * K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iSobaAHN","text_ar":"اـِصْبَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSobaHN","text_ar":"مُصْبَحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K [or perhaps the last should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSobaHN","text_ar":"مَصْبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Daybreak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dawn;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fajorN","text_ar":"فَجْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, Msb, K;) i. e. (so in the Msb, but in the K “ or ”) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beginning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part, of day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iSobaAHN","text_ar":"اـِصْبَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n. [inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaHa","text_ar":"اَصْبَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuboH","text_ar":"صُبْح"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur vi. 96, (Jel,) and is similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibokaArN","text_ar":"اـِبْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSobaHN","text_ar":"مُصْبَحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. of place and time from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaHa","text_ar":"اَصْبَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuboHN","text_ar":"صُبْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaAHN","text_ar":"اَصْبَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and thus some read in the Kur vi. 96. (Bd.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaHu","text_ar":"اَصْبَحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu liSuboHi","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ لِصُبْحِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAmisapK","text_ar":"خَامِسَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAmsp","text_ar":"خامسة"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liSiboHi","text_ar":"لِصِبْحِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the morning"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaAH","text_ar":"صَبَاح"},{"kind":"text","text":") ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the last"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of five days;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a fifth day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK;) [or rather,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a fifth night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as the last word is fem.;] like as one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"limuisoYi xAmsp","text_ar":"لِمُِسْىِ خامسة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1642},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~uboHu","text_ar":"الصُّبْحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The truth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plain, thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 449.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u SuboHK","text_ar":"اُمُّ صُبْحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is one of the names of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mekkeh."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","Jel","S"]},{"entry_id":"n23635","headword_ar":"صِبْحٌ","root":"SbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23636","headword_ar":"صَبَحٌ","root":"SbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuboHapN","text_ar":"صُبْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glistening"},{"kind":"text","text":"of iron (K, TA) and of other things. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]}}